---
title: Italian-Style Beef & Pesto Meatballs with Spaghetti & Parmesan
description: Change what you know about meatballs by adding a dollop of basil pesto to your mixture for an easy way to add flavour and unbeatable texture. Serve them up with a simple tomato sauce on top of spaghetti and don't forget to add the cheese!
